{"tid":1420462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民間發佈會不代表我 謝絕大台！","createTime":"2019-08-06T04:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T11:15:46.000Z","uid":188721,"like":9,"dislike":234,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"7b3b84a68df07342cf47254b6ff324646c013881","tid":1420462,"uid":188721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:39:31.000Z","msg":"即使我同意其內容，「民間發佈會」不能代表我。民間發佈會牽涉幾多人有份參與，就只代表參與的人。所以我希望他們能正名為「連登發佈會」或其他類似名目，勿盜竊「民間」一詞以挾民意。<br />\n<br />\n尤其是，當政府每日 press con，你又 press con，自然你就成為民間代表。這不就是大台嗎？<br />\n<br />\n沒有大台，就沒有談判對象，就不會被出賣。<br />\n不是我針對他們，而且我針對大台這件事。"},{"pid":"273dea54257d3c383387f8be9d0b91b4703c25d5","tid":1420462,"uid":188721,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:42:25.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"c4713c81cdf73a249706f2794035228f712798ad","tid":1420462,"uid":188721,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:42:35.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"78595e9f5cf29c1aea491550102da0245d6dfb8f","tid":1420462,"uid":188721,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:42:46.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"2e8bd1693d0a7c5e711063293c0cfc4589bba015","tid":1420462,"uid":188721,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:42:56.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"dbad70e2259a70f7d143ff9342640f6a558ce67c","tid":1420462,"uid":188721,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:43:06.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"778c66e94be09b5fb432e576e18f5cee217abe8f","tid":1420462,"uid":188721,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:43:16.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"f8488400d6c534041f79946e0acbb3e6e9901bd7","tid":1420462,"uid":997,"like":24,"dislike":3,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:43:25.000Z","msg":"有病去睇醫生啦<br />\n乜撚都話大台"},{"pid":"f6b6bbe056272d224641aec9c3f583fb5aa9e51d","tid":1420462,"uid":188721,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:43:49.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"8d243d577fb28bf